title: Dakota Johnson, Kate Winslet, Amy Schumer & More Named Elle's Women in Hollywood Honorees
text: Elle magazine has announced their Women in Hollywood honorees via their November 2015 covers: Ava DuVernay, Dakota Johnson, Carey Mulligan, Salma Hayek, Gena Rowlands, Amy Schumer, Alicia Vikander, and Kate Winslet! Here’s what the ladies had to share with the mag: Dakota, on making her Fifty Shades character funny: “I needed Anastasia to be funny. [...] »
